{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1697-04_010","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Sur la Nouvelle Capitation d’Angleterre","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", avril 1697 [tome 4], p. 10-18.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Personne n’ignore à combien de differens moyens on a tous les jours recours en Angleterre, pour trouver des fonds qui puissent fournir à ce que la guerre y cause de dépenses extraordinaires. Outre les Imposts qu’on y a mis sur toutes sortes de denrées, on a imposé aux Peuples une nouvelle Capitation, suivant laquelle les gens qui ne sont pas mariez, sont taxez comme s’ils avoient une Femme &amp; trois Enfans. C’est ce qui a donné lieu à ces Vers de M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" de S. Evremont. Ce nom ne sçauroit manquer de vous donner beaucoup d’empressement pour les lire.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"SUR LA NOUVELLE","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"Capitation d’Angleterre.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comment payer les taxes ordonnées ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comment sortir d’un si grand embaras ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Payons pourtant, &amp; ne nous plaignons pas.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que puissions-nous les payer dix années !","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On me dira, vos revenus sont courts.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Malaisément pourrez-vous satisfaire ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais je crains moins pour eux que pour mes jours,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vivre est pour moi la plus pressante affaire.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" J’ay vécu quatre-vingt-quatre ans","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Sans connoistre le mariage,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Heureux sans Femme &amp; sans Enfans,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Et voicy qu’au bout de mon âge,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il faut payer pour une &amp; pour trois descendans,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans avoir jamais eu ny Femme ny lignage.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais la taxe a son fondement,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Quand on en juge sainement.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Comment, vous n’avez point de femme ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Exempt de domestique bruit :","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Exempt du soupçon dont une ame","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Est sans repos &amp; jour &amp; nuit ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Exempt de la vaine dépence,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De la folle magnificence,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Du luxe aux maisons introduit","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Acquittez vous de bonne grace,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Vous qui n’estes point mariez,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Payez sans en estre priez,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de Maris voudroient payer en vostre place !","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Payez donc, payez de bon cœur","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" La taxe de vostre bonheur.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[14]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Un discours ennuyeux de modes,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" D’Engageantes &amp; de Commodes,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" D’habits ou commandez ou faits,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ne vous importune jamais.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’air trop libre d’une Coquette,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" D’une Galante peu discrete","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Les appetits trop naturels,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ne vous donnent aucune atteinte.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Fasse qui voudra des Noëls,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Vous pourrez les chanter sans crainte.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Payez donc, payez de bon cœur","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La taxe de vostre bonheur.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[11]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avoir une Epouse éternelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aux yeux des autres toujours belle,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et seul en estre dégoûté","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand chacun en est enchanté.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cependant jaloux &amp; sincere","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avec chagrin la regarder,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et plus on a soin de luy plaire,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus on prend soin de la garder.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est là, c’est le charmant usage,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est la douceur du mariage.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous qui n’estes point mariez,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Payez sans en estre priez.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[11]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tantost un Epoux difficile","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’a chez luy que severité :","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tantost le même trop docile,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’a pas sa propre volonté.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mal à propos rude ou facile,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il ôte ou perd sa liberté,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vous serez toujours tranquille","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans une sage égalité,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vous vous moquerez des chaîne.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ceux dont je décris les peines.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Payez, &amp; payez de bon cœur","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La taxe de vostre bonheur.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[11]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" On voit arriver d’ordinaire","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qu’un Mary souhaite un garçon,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qui voudra la mort de son pere,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour se trouver plûtost maistre de la maison.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Je ne parle point d’une fille,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De ce Sexe discret &amp; doux :","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais je conseille à la Famille","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De luy vouloir choisir promptement un Epoux.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Acquitez vous de bonne grace,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Vous qui n’estes point mariez,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Payez sans en estre priez.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de Maris voudroient payer en vostre place !","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[11]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Après tout, Monsieur Colt, pensez","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que quatre-vingt-quatre ans passez,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sont comme la fin de la vie","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui de l’éternelle est suivie.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi vous n’avez pas de tort,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans les taxes que l’on impose,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De vouloir me traiter de mort.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un mort ne paie aucune chose.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand je demande, un Debiteur.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur ce beau prétexte se fonde,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que je dois estre hors du monde,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et l’on me traite d’imposteur.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[20]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une tres-vertueuse Dame,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus devote, s’il se pouvoit,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A fait prier Dieu pour mon ame","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’argent qu’elle me devoit.","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[22]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par cette pieuse assurance","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’on me donne de mon trépas,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’entre moi-même en défiance","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si je suis, si je ne suis pas.","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[24]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A mon âge ce n’est pas vivre,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Monsieur Colt, mes sens sont perclus.","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Effacez-moi de vostre Livre,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dites que je ne suis plus.","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}}]}}}